# QR Cafe Ordering System ☕📱

A QR-based cafe menu and ordering system built using Python and Flask. 
Customers can scan a QR code to view the cafe menu and place their order directly from their mobile device.

## Features

- QR code menu access
- Mobile-friendly ordering
- Multiple menu items
- Automatic bill calculation
- Orders displayed in server terminal

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Flask
- QRCode
- Pillow

## Installation

Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/qr-cafe-ordering-system.git

Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run the server

python app.py

Generate QR code

python qr_generator.py

## How It Works

1. Start the Flask server.
2. Generate a QR code using the generator script.
3. Customers scan the QR code.
4. Menu opens on their phone.
5. They select items and place an order.
6. Orders appear in the server console.

